headline: BlackRock price target raised to $1,133 from $1,105 at Deutsche Bank
summary: Deutsche Bank raised the firm’s price target on BlackRock (BLK) to $1,133 from $1,105 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. Following the U.S. elections, the firm made several updates to its macro assumptions in its brokers, asset managers and exchanges models. Deutsche views the macro backdrop into at least 2025 as potentially fostering greater capital markets activity, with at least average positive equity market returns, supported by fiscal stimulus and potentially lighter regulation.
